{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bdb164a65b","title":"中原军以机动灵活之行动在外线牵制敌人","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e68e5f2782","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":13,"articleId":"bdb164a65b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji4","name":"毛泽东文集第四卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji4":{"comments":[{"id":"55eefb3087","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"},{"id":"e9342e1673","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b","index":1,"part_index":1,"offset":3,"text":"郑、李，指郑位三、李先念，当时分别任中原军区政治委员和司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ada51316e8","type":"title","text":"中原军以机动灵活之行动在外线牵制敌人","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b"},{"id":"e9342e1673","type":"appellation","text":"郑、李：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b"},{"id":"b3180b51fa","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）蒋介石决心大打，其计划是先攻苏皖，后攻华北，并企图消灭我中原军。其攻苏皖之计划定于数日内行动，分为三路，一路由徐州向南，一路由津浦向东，一路由江北向北，同时向我苏皖边区进攻，总兵力在二十师以上。（二）我党决心粉碎反动派的进攻，争取胜利，取得和平。（三）我中原军之任务是以机动灵活之行动，在鄂、豫、皖、川、陕广大地境内，在外线牵制反动派大量军队，帮助我内线作战部队取得胜利，是为作战之第一阶段；然后我内线部队渡淮向南，与中原军会合，夺取信阳、大别山、安庆之线，是为第二阶段。（四）上述计划务守秘密。（五）此电阅后即毁。（六）你们行动计划望告。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b"},{"id":"2640422a83","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b"},{"id":"52dcd3e68c","type":"paragraph","text":"午元","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b"}],"page":{"id":"39e54b736f","publicationId":"wenji4","articleId":"bdb164a65b","start":169,"end":169}}}},"__N_SSG":true}